OL,3,CCouncil tax up and energy bills down:
OL,4,CHousehold bill changes coming in April
OL,6,FThe will fall by 12% on 1 April 2024,
OL,7,Fto #1,690 a year for a typical dual-
OL,8,Ffuel household paying by Direct Debit
OL,9,F(based on Ofgem's new, lower typical
OL,10,Fuse figures).JThe price cap will last
OL,11,Ffor three months. It is predicted to
OL,12,Ffall again in July 2024.
