OL,3,CCouncil tax up and energy bills down:
OL,4,CHousehold bill changes coming in April
OL,6,FCouncil tax is a fee you pay which
OL,7,Fhelps councils pay for the services
OL,8,Fthey provide.
OL,10,FExamples include bin collection,
OL,11,Flibraries, maintaining parks and
OL,12,Fsports centres, highway services,
OL,13,Fincluding street lighting and
OL,14,Fcleaning, and road maintenance.
OL,16,FThe amount of council tax you pay is
OL,17,Fdecided on which valuation band your
OL,18,Fproperty is, your personal
OL,19,Fcircumstances and how much the council
OL,20,Fneeds to fund its services.
