OL,3,CCouncil tax up and energy bills down:
OL,4,CHousehold bill changes coming in April
OL,6,FThe Household Support Fund has
OL,7,Fsupported millions of people during
OL,8,Fthe cost of living crisis, but it is
OL,9,Flikely to be scrapped.
OL,11,FGrants from the fund have been awarded
OL,12,Fto struggling families to help pay for
OL,13,Ffood, heating and other essentials.
OL,15,FThe current phase of the fund will
OL,16,Ffinish at the end of March, and it
OL,17,Fdoesn't look likely to be renewed.
OL,19,FThe pot of funding comes from
OL,20,Fgovernment, but the money is
OL,21,Fdistributed by local councils.
